description:
This is a 30 minute workout called 'TOTAL UPPER BODY WORKOUT: ARMS + CHEST + SHOULDERS + BACK' from the channel Roberta's Gym.
The workout falls under Strength/Body weight and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Disciplined Grind and The Progression Quest vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Are you ready to burn your upper body fat? 

This workout is a highly intensive exercise designed to work your back and chest muscles in order to burn the fat and tone your muscles! 

The workout doesn't require a gym or special weights - you can do it easily at home! But like any workout, you need to be disciplined to perform this training. You need to do this everyday if you want to see the results that this workout is offering.
